\begin_inset Formula $\class{OD}(T)$
\end_inset

.
 Kunen's proof of Theorem 2.2 works with essentially no modification â€“ other than requiring 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta>\mathrm{rk}(T)$
\end_inset

 as well.
 There's something here that could be dug into about sequences 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

